[SN]TITLE[SN]
Australian boy gets new home after bushfire burnt it down

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Imagine losing your home and everything you own in a massive fire.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
26 January 2015 Last updated at 08:54 GMT
That happened to 12-year-old Cameron Orton whose home was totally destroyed by wildfires in Australia last year.
It's a problem the country faces every summer.
The BBC's Phil Mercer went to meet him.
